#COUNTS OF ALL CONTACTS

SOURCE_COUNT<-TO_DATE %>% 
  select(SOURCE) %>%
  group_by(SOURCE) %>%
  tally()

GENDER_COUNT <-TO_DATE %>% 
  select(GENDER) %>%
  group_by(GENDER) %>%
  tally()

AGE_COUNT <- TO_DATE %>% 
  select(AGE) %>%
  group_by(AGE) %>%
  tally()

SCREEN_COMPLETE_COUNT <- TO_DATE %>% 
  select(SCREEN_COMPLETEYN) %>%
  group_by(SCREEN_COMPLETEYN) %>%
  tally()
